<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Climate Calculators</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* SITE STYLES */
        body { font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fdfdfd; color: #333; padding-top: 80px; }
        h1 { color: #175226; margin: 30px auto 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #175226; padding-bottom: 10px; width: 95%; max-width: 1400px; text-align: left; }
        
        .controls-container { width: 95%; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .language-row { margin-bottom: 15px; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
        .row-plant { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .input-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; width: 100%; min-width: 200px; flex: 1; }
        
        label { margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; color: #175226; font-size: 14px; }
        select { padding: 10px; font-size: 15px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; background: #fff; width: 100%; }
        
        .toggle-container { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #175226; background: #e8f5e9; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 4px; white-space: nowrap; }
        .btn-download { background: #175226; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-download:hover { background: #2e7d32; }
        
        #compatibility { font-size: 16px; color: #175226; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; background: #e8f5e9; border-left: 5px solid #175226; border-radius: 4px; max-width: 1400px; width: 95%; box-sizing: border-box;}
        
        #desktop-results { flex-grow: 1; min-height: 400px; overflow: auto; margin: 10px auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); position: relative; width: 95%; max-width: 1400px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        #desktop-results table { width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; }
        #desktop-results th { background: #175226; color: white; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; padding: 12px 15px; border-right: 1px solid #0d3b18; border-bottom: 1px solid #0d3b18; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; }
        #desktop-results td { border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; border-right: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px 15px; vertical-align: top; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; min-width: 120px; background: #fff; }
        
        #mobile-results { width: 95%; margin: 0 auto; box-sizing: border-box; }
        #mobile-results .plant-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        #mobile-results .plant-table th, #mobile-results .plant-table td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; word-wrap: break-word; }
        #mobile-results .plant-table th { background: #175226; color: white; }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) { #desktop-results { display: none; } #mobile-results { display: block; } }
        @media (min-width: 769px) { #mobile-results { display: none; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Climate Calculators</h1>
    <div id="calcBlock1"></div>
    
    <!-- Crop DLI ↔ PPFD Converter -->
    <details id="cropConverter">
      <summary>Crop DLI ↔ PPFD Converter <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>Convert between Daily Light Integral (DLI) and Photosynthetic Photon Flux Density (PPFD) with crop selection.</p>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="cropSelect" title="Select a crop to auto-fill typical values">Select Crop/Category:</label>
        <select id="cropSelect" onchange="cropOnSelect()">
          <option value="">-- Choose a Crop/Category --</option>
          <optgroup label="Greenhouse">
            <option value="ghVeg">Leafy Greens / Herbs (Veg)</option>
            <option value="ghFlower">Flowering Crops (Peppers/Tomatoes)</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup label="Indoors">
            <option value="indoorMicrogreens">Microgreens</option>
            <option value="indoorVeg">Leafy Greens / Herbs (Veg)</option>
            <option value="indoorFlower">Flowering Crops</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup label="Common Edibles">
            <option value="tomato">Tomato</option>
            <option value="pepper">Pepper</option>
            <option value="cucumber">Cucumber</option>
            <option value="cannabisVeg">Cannabis (Veg)</option>
            <option value="cannabisFlower">Cannabis (Flower)</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup label="Potted Plants">
            <option value="orchid">Orchid / Phalaenopsis</option>
            <option value="dendrobium">Dendrobium</option>
            <option value="bromelia">Bromelia</option>
            <option value="anthurium">Anthurium</option>
            <option value="kalanchoe">Kalanchoe</option>
          </optgroup>
          <optgroup label="Cut Flowers">
            <option value="cutChrysanthemum">Chrysanthemum (cut)</option>
            <option value="cutRose">Rose (cut)</option>
            <option value="lily">Lily (cut)</option>
            <option value="lisianthus">Lisianthus (cut)</option>
            <option value="alstroemeria">Alstroemeria (cut)</option>
          </optgroup>
          <option value="custom">Custom / Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="hoursInput">Photoperiod (hrs):</label>
        <input type="number" id="hoursInput" placeholder="e.g., 16">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="ppfdInput">PPFD (µmol/m²/s):</label>
        <input type="number" id="ppfdInput" step="0.01" placeholder="Enter or auto-fill">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="dliInput">DLI (mol/m²/day):</label>
        <input type="number" id="dliInput" step="0.01" placeholder="Enter or auto-fill">
      </div>
      <div class="field" style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="cropCalculateDLI()">Calculate DLI</button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="cropCalculatePPFD()">Calculate PPFD</button>
      </div>
      <div id="resultOutput" class="result"></div>
      <div id="notesOutput" class="notes" style="display:none;"></div>
    </details>
    
    <!-- DLI for Electric Light Calculator -->
    <details id="electricLightDLI">
      <summary>DLI for Electric Light Calculator <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>Compute DLI from an electric light’s intensity.</p>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="lightIntensity">Light intensity (µmol/m²/s):</label>
        <input type="number" id="lightIntensity" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 200">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="photoperiod">Photoperiod (hrs):</label>
        <input type="number" id="photoperiod" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 16">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="electricDliOutput">DLI (mol/m²/day):</label>
        <input type="text" id="electricDliOutput" readonly>
      </div>
      <div class="field" style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="calculateElectricDLI()">Calculate DLI</button>
      </div>
    </details>
    
    <!-- Estimate DLI from Peak Sunlight Calculator -->
    <details id="sunlightDLI">
      <summary>Estimate DLI from Peak Sunlight Calculator <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>Estimate DLI based on peak sunlight at solar noon.</p>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Light Units:</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sunlightUnit" value="ppfd" checked> µmol/m²/s</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sunlightUnit" value="watts"> Watts/m²</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sunlightUnit" value="lux"> Lux</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="sunlightUnit" value="footcandles"> Footcandles</label>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="sunPeakValue">Peak sunlight level:</label>
        <input type="number" id="sunPeakValue" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 2000">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="sunriseTime">Sunrise (HHMM):</label>
        <input type="text" id="sunriseTime" placeholder="e.g., 0600">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="sunsetTime">Sunset (HHMM):</label>
        <input type="text" id="sunsetTime" placeholder="e.g., 1800">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="sunDliOutput">Estimated DLI (mol/m²/day):</label>
        <input type="number" id="sunDliOutput" readonly>
      </div>
      <div class="field" style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="calculateSunlightDLI()">Calculate DLI</button>
      </div>
    </details>
    
    <!-- Graph: DLI vs Photoperiod -->
    <details id="dliGraphSection">
      <summary>Graph: DLI vs Photoperiod <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>See how DLI changes with photoperiod for a given PPFD.</p>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="graphPPFD">PPFD for Graph (µmol/m²/s):</label>
        <input type="number" id="graphPPFD" step="0.01" placeholder="e.g., 300">
      </div>
      <div class="field" style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="drawGraph()">Draw Graph</button>
      </div>
      <canvas id="dliGraph" width="700" height="300"></canvas>
    </details>
    
    <!-- Vapor Pressure Deficit (VPD) Calculator -->
    <details id="vpdCalculator">
      <summary>Vapor Pressure Deficit (VPD) Calculator <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>Calculate VPD based on temperature and relative humidity.</p>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Temperature Units:</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdTempUnit" value="c" checked> °C</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdTempUnit" value="f"> °F</label>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Pressure Units:</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdPressUnit" value="kPa" checked> kPa</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdPressUnit" value="Pa"> Pa</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdPressUnit" value="atm"> atm</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdPressUnit" value="mbar"> mbar</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="vpdPressUnit" value="bar"> bar</label>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="rhVPD">Relative Humidity (%):</label>
        <input type="number" id="rhVPD" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 60">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="airTempVPD">Air Temperature:</label>
        <input type="number" id="airTempVPD" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 25">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="leafTempVPD">Leaf Temperature (optional):</label>
        <input type="number" id="leafTempVPD" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 26">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="vpdOutput">VPD:</label>
        <input type="text" id="vpdOutput" readonly>
      </div>
      <div class="field" style="text-align:center;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="calculateVPD()">Calculate VPD</button>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Climate Calculators Script -->
  <script>
    const SHAPE_FACTOR = 0.5;
    const CONVERSION_FACTORS = { ppfd: 1, watts: 2.0, lux: 0.0185, footcandles: 0.2 };

    /* Crop DLI ↔ PPFD functions */
    const cropData = {
      "ghVeg": { name: "Greenhouse - Leafy Greens/Herbs", recommendedDLI: "≥17", minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null },
      "ghFlower": { name: "Greenhouse - Flowering (Peppers/Tomatoes)", recommendedDLI: "20-40", minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null },
      "indoorMicrogreens": { name: "Indoors - Microgreens", recommendedDLI: "6-12", minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null },
      "indoorVeg": { name: "Indoors - Leafy Greens/Herbs", recommendedDLI: "12-17", minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null },
      "indoorFlower": { name: "Indoors - Flowering Crops", recommendedDLI: "15-40", minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null },
      "tomato": { name: "Tomato", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 170, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 270 },
      "pepper": { name: "Pepper", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 120, maxPPFD: 300, typicalPPFD: 230 },
      "cucumber": { name: "Cucumber", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 120, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 230 },
      "cannabisVeg": { name: "Cannabis (Vegetative)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 280, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 300 },
      "cannabisFlower": { name: "Cannabis (Flowering)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 650, maxPPFD: 1500, typicalPPFD: 1000 },
      "orchid": { name: "Orchid / Phalaenopsis", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 80, maxPPFD: 230, typicalPPFD: 160 },
      "dendrobium": { name: "Dendrobium", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 130, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 200 },
      "bromelia": { name: "Bromelia", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 40, maxPPFD: 120, typicalPPFD: 90 },
      "anthurium": { name: "Anthurium", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 60, maxPPFD: 120, typicalPPFD: 90 },
      "kalanchoe": { name: "Kalanchoe", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 60, maxPPFD: 120, typicalPPFD: 90 },
      "cutChrysanthemum": { name: "Chrysanthemum (cut)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 105, maxPPFD: 220, typicalPPFD: 140 },
      "cutRose": { name: "Rose (cut)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 170, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 220 },
      "lily": { name: "Lily (cut)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 180, maxPPFD: 350, typicalPPFD: 230 },
      "lisianthus": { name: "Lisianthus (cut)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 70, maxPPFD: 150, typicalPPFD: 90 },
      "alstroemeria": { name: "Alstroemeria (cut)", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: 70, maxPPFD: 120, typicalPPFD: 90 },
      "custom": { name: "Custom / Other", recommendedDLI: null, minPPFD: null, maxPPFD: null, typicalPPFD: null }
    };
    function cropOnSelect() {
      const selected = document.getElementById('cropSelect').value;
      const data = cropData[selected] || null;
      const ppfdField = document.getElementById('ppfdInput');
      const dliField = document.getElementById('dliInput');
      const notesDiv = document.getElementById('notesOutput');
      ppfdField.value = "";
      dliField.value = "";
      notesDiv.style.display = "none";
      notesDiv.innerHTML = "";
      if (!data) return;
      if (data.typicalPPFD) { ppfdField.value = data.typicalPPFD; }
      let noteText = `<strong>${data.name}</strong><br/>`;
      if (data.minPPFD || data.maxPPFD) {
        noteText += `Min PPFD: ${data.minPPFD ?? "-"}, Max PPFD: ${data.maxPPFD ?? "-"}, Typical: ${data.typicalPPFD ?? "-"}`;
      }
      if (data.recommendedDLI) {
        noteText += (data.minPPFD || data.maxPPFD ? "<br/>" : "") + `Recommended DLI: ${data.recommendedDLI}`;
      }
      if (noteText) { notesDiv.style.display = "block"; notesDiv.innerHTML = noteText; }
    }
    function cropCalculateDLI() {
      const ppfdValue = parseFloat(document.getElementById('ppfdInput').value);
      const hours = parseFloat(document.getElementById('hoursInput').value);
      const resultDiv = document.getElementById('resultOutput');
      if (isNaN(ppfdValue) || isNaN(hours) || hours <= 0) {
        resultDiv.textContent = "Please enter valid numbers for PPFD and photoperiod.";
        return;
      }
      const dli = (ppfdValue * hours * 3600) / 1e6;
      document.getElementById('dliInput').value = dli.toFixed(2);
      resultDiv.textContent = `DLI = ${dli.toFixed(2)} mol/m²/day`;
    }
    function cropCalculatePPFD() {
      const dliValue = parseFloat(document.getElementById('dliInput').value);
      const hours = parseFloat(document.getElementById('hoursInput').value);
      const resultDiv = document.getElementById('resultOutput');
      if (isNaN(dliValue) || isNaN(hours) || hours <= 0) {
        resultDiv.textContent = "Please enter valid numbers for DLI and photoperiod.";
        return;
      }
      const ppfd = (dliValue * 1e6) / (hours * 3600);
      document.getElementById('ppfdInput').value = ppfd.toFixed(2);
      resultDiv.textContent = `PPFD = ${ppfd.toFixed(2)} µmol/m²/s`;
    }
    
    /* DLI for Electric Light */
    function calculateElectricDLI() {
      const intensity = parseFloat(document.getElementById('lightIntensity').value) || 0;
      const photoperiod = parseFloat(document.getElementById('photoperiod').value) || 0;
      let dli = intensity * photoperiod * 3600 * 1e-6;
      dli = Math.round(dli * 100) / 100;
      document.getElementById('electricDliOutput').value = dli;
    }
    
    /* Estimate DLI from Peak Sunlight */
    function calculateSunlightDLI() {
      const unitElems = document.getElementsByName('sunlightUnit');
      let selectedUnit = 'ppfd';
      for (let i = 0; i < unitElems.length; i++) {
        if (unitElems[i].checked) { selectedUnit = unitElems[i].value; break; }
      }
      const peakValue = parseFloat(document.getElementById('sunPeakValue').value) || 0;
      const peakPPFD = peakValue * (CONVERSION_FACTORS[selectedUnit] || 1);
      const sunriseStr = document.getElementById('sunriseTime').value.trim();
      const sunsetStr = document.getElementById('sunsetTime').value.trim();
      const sunriseDecimal = parseInt(sunriseStr.substring(0,2),10) + ((parseInt(sunriseStr.substring(2,4),10)||0)/60);
      const sunsetDecimal = parseInt(sunsetStr.substring(0,2),10) + ((parseInt(sunsetStr.substring(2,4),10)||0)/60);
      let dayLength = sunsetDecimal - sunriseDecimal;
      if (dayLength < 0) dayLength = 0;
      const dayLengthSeconds = dayLength * 3600;
      let dli = SHAPE_FACTOR * peakPPFD * dayLengthSeconds * 1e-6;
      dli = Math.round(dli * 100) / 100;
      document.getElementById('sunDliOutput').value = dli;
    }
    
    /* Vapor Pressure Deficit (VPD) */
    function calculateVPD() {
      const tempElems = document.getElementsByName('vpdTempUnit');
      let tempUnit = 'c';
      for (let i = 0; i < tempElems.length; i++) {
        if (tempElems[i].checked) { tempUnit = tempElems[i].value; break; }
      }
      const pressElems = document.getElementsByName('vpdPressUnit');
      let pressUnit = 'kPa';
      for (let i = 0; i < pressElems.length; i++) {
        if (pressElems[i].checked) { pressUnit = pressElems[i].value; break; }
      }
      const rh = parseFloat(document.getElementById('rhVPD').value) || 0;
      let airTemp = parseFloat(document.getElementById('airTempVPD').value) || 0;
      let leafTemp = parseFloat(document.getElementById('leafTempVPD').value);
      if (tempUnit === 'f') {
        airTemp = (airTemp - 32) * 5/9;
        if (!isNaN(leafTemp)) { leafTemp = (leafTemp - 32) * 5/9; }
      }
      function saturationVaporPressureCelsius(Tc) {
        return 0.6108 * Math.exp((17.27 * Tc) / (Tc + 237.3));
      }
      const esAir = saturationVaporPressureCelsius(airTemp);
      const ea = (rh / 100) * esAir;
      let vpd = !isNaN(leafTemp) ? saturationVaporPressureCelsius(leafTemp) - ea : esAir - ea;
      function convertFromKPa(value, targetUnit) {
        switch (targetUnit) {
          case 'kPa': return value;
          case 'Pa': return value * 1000;
          case 'atm': return value / 101.325;
          case 'mbar': return value * 10;
          case 'bar': return value / 100;
          default: return value;
        }
      }
      const vpdConverted = convertFromKPa(vpd, pressUnit);
      const vpdRounded = Math.round(vpdConverted * 1000) / 1000;
      document.getElementById('vpdOutput').value = vpdRounded + " " + pressUnit;
    }
    
    /* Graph: DLI vs Photoperiod */
    function drawGraph() {
      const ppfd = parseFloat(document.getElementById('graphPPFD').value);
      const canvas = document.getElementById('dliGraph');
      const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
      if (isNaN(ppfd) || ppfd <= 0) {
        alert("Please enter a valid PPFD value for the graph.");
        return;
      }
      ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
      const padding = 40;
      const width = canvas.width - padding * 2;
      const height = canvas.height - padding * 2;
      const maxDLI = (ppfd * 24 * 3600) / 1e6;
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(padding, padding);
      ctx.lineTo(padding, canvas.height - padding);
      ctx.lineTo(canvas.width - padding, canvas.height - padding);
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.font = "12px Arial";
      ctx.fillStyle = "#000";
      ctx.textAlign = "center";
      for (let i = 0; i <= 24; i += 4) {
        const x = padding + (i / 24) * width;
        ctx.fillText(i + " hrs", x, canvas.height - padding + 15);
      }
      ctx.textAlign = "right";
      for (let d = 0; d <= maxDLI; d += maxDLI / 4) {
        const y = canvas.height - padding - (d / maxDLI) * height;
        ctx.fillText(d.toFixed(1), padding - 5, y + 3);
      }
      ctx.beginPath();
      for (let hr = 0; hr <= 24; hr += 0.1) {
        const dli = (ppfd * hr * 3600) / 1e6;
        const x = padding + (hr / 24) * width;
        const y = canvas.height - padding - (dli / maxDLI) * height;
        if (hr === 0) ctx.moveTo(x, y); else ctx.lineTo(x, y);
      }
      ctx.strokeStyle = "#2c7fb8";
      ctx.stroke();
    }
  </script>
</body>






























































<body>
  <h1>Combined Garden &amp; Fertilizer Calculators</h1>
  <div id="calcBlock2">
    <!-- 1. Bed Dimension Increase Calculator (Garden Bed Calculators) -->
    <details class="toggleable">
      <summary>
        Bed Dimension Increase Calculator <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span>
      </summary>
      <p>Enter current dimensions and % increase.</p>
      <label>Unit System:
        <select id="bedUnit">
          <option value="m" selected>Meters</option>
          <option value="ft">Feet</option>
          <option value="in">Inches</option>
          <option value="cm">Centimeters</option>
        </select>
      </label>
      <label>Current Length:
        <input type="number" id="bed_currentLength" placeholder="e.g., 2.225">
      </label>
      <label>Current Width:
        <input type="number" id="bed_currentWidth" placeholder="e.g., 1.321">
      </label>
      <label>Current Depth:
        <input type="number" id="bed_currentDepth" placeholder="e.g., 0.127">
      </label>
      <label>Increase by (%):
        <input type="number" id="bed_increasePercent" placeholder="e.g., 10">
      </label>
      <button onclick="calculateBedAdjustment()">Calculate Adjusted Bed</button>
      <div id="bedAdjResults"></div>
    </details>

    <!-- 2. Cost of Nutrient Application Rate Calculator (Additional Fertilizer & Nutrient Calculators) -->
    <details class="toggleable">
      <summary>
        Cost of Nutrient Application Rate Calculator <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span>
      </summary>
      <p>Compute total cost based on bag price, bag size, nutrient proportion, area, and application rate.</p>
      <label>Price per Bag ($):
        <input type="number" id="costBagPrice" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 49">
      </label>
      <div>
        <label>Bag Size Unit:
          <select id="costBagSizeUnit">
            <option value="kg" selected>kg</option>
            <option value="lb">lb</option>
            <option value="g">g</option>
            <option value="oz">oz</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label>Bag Size:
          <input type="number" id="costBagSize" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 23">
        </label>
      </div>
      <label>Nutrient Proportion (%):
        <input type="number" id="costNutrientProp" step="any" placeholder="e.g., 30">
