    <!-- Lumens to PPF Converter -->
    <details id="lumensToPPF">
      <summary>Lumens to PPF (µmol/s) Converter <span class="toggle-text">(Open/Close)</span></summary>
      <p>Convert lumens to photosynthetic photon flux (PPF) in µmol/s using a selectable light spectrum.</p>
